data.description: This stunning updated pool home is located in Greenbriar Village!  The cozy front porch welcomes you to this quaint home. The open floorplan, great room with gas fireplace, and updated kitchen with white cabinets await you.  The Master features his and her closets, an updated main bath with dual vanities, a large soaking tub, and a beautiful tiled shower.   Don't miss out on the backyard it feels like an oasis with a large patio, pool, and landscape.  Make this your home today!
